sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Source Repos
    participant GH as GitHub Action
    participant P as Parser
    participant M as Mastodon
    participant B as Buffer
    participant DT as dev.to
    participant U as User

    GH->>S: collect POST.it.md / POST.en.md
    GH->>GH: commit & push new posts
    GH->>P: parse _posts/*.en.md
    P->>P: validate, build social text
    P->>GH: posts.json
    alt dry_run = false
        GH->>M: publish posts (skip if already posted)
        GH->>B: queue drafts per channel (skip if already queued)
        GH->>DT: create drafts (skip if title/article missing)
        U->>B: review, edit and approve
        U->>DT: review, edit and publish
    else dry_run = true
        GH->>M: check dedup, skip publish
        GH->>B: check dedup, skip queue
        GH->>DT: check dedup, skip create
    end
